<div2>
<lb ed="C I" n="0068b01"/><p id="pI01p0068b0101">夫玄&CB07538;妙寂。&CB00644;末世<note n="0068001" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30519;＝所【史】</note><app n="0068001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">所</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30519;</rdg></app>能顯
<lb ed="C I" n="0068b02"/>其元。真景疑槨。非季俗之<app source="0068001" type="＊"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">所</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30519;</rdg></app>
<lb ed="C I" n="0068b03"/>宣其皇。是以&CB00425;若之智難昇
<lb ed="C I" n="0068b04"/>岨皆之葙。故<note n="0068002" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30520;＝顯【史】</note><app n="0068002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">顯</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30520;</rdg></app>神&CB30521;歸敬慈
<lb ed="C I" n="0068b05"/>萇者矣。但聖藏淟澄洪<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">臨</unclear>道
<lb ed="C I" n="0068b06"/>一&CB00644;可寶塔云重&CB31156;&CB30522;寶輻
<lb ed="C I" n="0068b07"/>海臻。&CB31155;像寸暈則無牛&CB00561;之
<lb ed="C I" n="0068b08"/>潤<note n="0068003" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30523;＝哉【史】</note><app n="0068003"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">哉</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30523;</rdg></app>。山岳摧巔。海獲崩竭。&CB00130;
<lb ed="C I" n="0068b09"/>神儀於清流之曲。葵永顏不
<lb ed="C I" n="0068b10"/>朽者也。<note n="0068004" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30524;＝豈【史】</note><app n="0068004"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">豈</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30524;</rdg></app>緣<note n="0068005" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30525;＝微【史】</note><app n="0068005"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">微</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30525;</rdg></app>工。當願正<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">備</unclear>。
<lb ed="C I" n="0068b11"/>遠通慈<note n="0068006" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB11823;＝朗【史】</note><app n="0068006"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">朗</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB11823;</rdg></app>。垢於<note n="0068007" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB05856;＝青【史】</note><app n="0068007"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">青</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB05856;</rdg></app>宮。
<lb ed="C I" n="0068b12"/>上為皇帝　陛下。國督祚康。
<lb ed="C I" n="0068b13"/>祚幾標式。合右拙塢村。<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">返</unclear>願
<lb ed="C I" n="0068b14"/>合邑七十人等。敬造室家石
<lb ed="C I" n="0068b15"/>像一區。直鍾薩提。願合邑<note n="0068008" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30526;＝仰【史】</note><app n="0068008"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">仰</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30526;</rdg></app>
<lb ed="C I" n="0068b16"/>隊七世。乃至<app source="0068001" type="＊"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">所</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30519;</rdg></app>生。朋<note n="0068009" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB08099;＝友【史】</note><app n="0068009"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">友</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB08099;</rdg></app>眷屬。
<lb ed="C I" n="0068b17"/>合霜奢梨。普洽私願。一時成
<lb ed="C I" n="0068b18"/>佛。　　天寶二年保莊嚴功德飛騎尉杜思福邑子董
<lb ed="C I" n="0068b19"/>建儀元年歲在毋申六月丁
<lb ed="C I" n="0068b20"/>亥朔廿八日甲寅日
<lb ed="C I" n="0068b21"/>願□主施□□</p>
</div2>
